Lord Stevens is to be investigated over allegations of a cover-up of police corruption in the bungled Step-hen Lawrence murder probe .
Independent Police Complaints Commission said it will investigate claims that the former Met chief failed to hand over key information to the Macpherson Inquiry regarding the teenager 's race hate killing .
The watchdog probe stems from a complaint from Stephen 's father Neville Lawrence .
Lord Stevens was deputy commissioner of the Metropolitan Police from 1998 to 2000 .